{"tid":698763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我係香港政府，下一步要玩死天琦會咁做","createTime":"2018-06-12T03:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T05:03:11.000Z","uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c927a7bd33cc0993dd66b007450f9bae6631bf5","tid":698763,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"行為良好會減刑，相反<br />\n如果囚犯獄中鬧事就會不斷加刑<br />\n<br />\n若果我係香港政府，會係咁搵人入獄不斷挑釁天琦，打佢又整傷自己，再唔係就搵多一個犯做partner老屈天琦都有份打人，然後齊齊加監，不斷loop呢個step,天琦出獄無期<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個無法無天既香港，呢個可能性已經唔再係鳩up，搵人叫天琦喺監獄見到啲囚犯有不軌眼神就即避啦，唔係實唔夠玩，隨時六年變三十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd3d982434f6c5c54052025649c4d892b58181e","tid":698763,"uid":140928,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"冇必要<br />\n6年後已經冇人記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12efa0cfe3ac2bab0a18f2d019b98d8ef908c78","tid":698763,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"大家點睇，如果你地想睇住佢，係咪應該組織義士犯啲細蟻罪例如坐幾星期至兩個月咁樣輪班入獄陪住天琦等佢唔好比人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c53ddbfd073646cc80e01253d124cbab148752","tid":698763,"uid":1751,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e12efa0cfe3ac2bab0a18f2d019b98d8ef908c78","tid":698763,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"大家點睇，如果你地想睇住佢，係咪應該組織義士犯啲細蟻罪例如坐幾星期至兩個月咁樣輪班入獄陪住天琦等佢唔好比人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5293ef76ba94d7